{"tid":378715,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[DSE maths] MC 其實唔難","createTime":"2017-08-28T16:42:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T12:58:13.000Z","uid":126679,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aa59c7c09210337738cf9c14fdf57e9fc8914b3a","tid":378715,"uid":126679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T16:42:29.000Z","msg":"大家好<br />\n最近好多人討論緊2017年既一條MC<br />\n咁我都分享下我 [其實唔難] 既做法啦<br />\n<br />\n計埋呢一條題目<br />\n[其實唔難] 系列已經有6條片了<br />\n都係分享返點樣可以真係做到 [唔識都啱]<br />\n希望大家會有所得著啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RxMCVTdk98E&amp;t\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRxMCVTdk98E%26t&d=TGuA74kbfzTUufBc9i%2FkiLr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=7fb0d910\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RxMCVTdk98E&amp;t</a><br />\n<br />\n除左數學科之外<br />\n我個平台仲會分享埋chemistry呢一科既內容既<br />\n兩個科目, 我都會分享好多好多 技巧 / concept / 部署 等等<br />\n如果真係覺得有用, 咁我就會繼續分享更多<br />\n<br />\n以下係我個facebook page<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dsechemathsbob/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdsechemathsbob%2F&d=TGuA74kbfzTUufBc9i%2FkiLr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=8918e2ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dsechemathsbob/</a><br />\n如果有任何關於 chemistry 或者 maths 既問題想問<br />\n或者想我拍d咩片黎幫大家<br />\n都歡迎inbox我話比我知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後祝各位<br />\ndse 順順利利<br />\n溫書溫得特別起勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9716157b13cdfe0b3ee41cf9576badef91b645f","tid":378715,"uid":125262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:12:33.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3215cd63289ff76e2ebd9a7a0cee8e1c0588745","tid":378715,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:23:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔識都啱，得啖笑"},{"pid":"0008a4218cd9821801accab868bf329335cdd61f","tid":378715,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:53:11.000Z","msg":"其實直接用4個ans代入4心prog<br />\n就自然揾到4個ans各自嘅in centre <br />\n再將4個in centre分別代入條eqt度<br />\nmatch到嗰個就係正確答案啦"},{"pid":"e0e2d52a9380415cac64750326cfa6235457d29d","tid":378715,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:58:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實直接用4個ans代入4心prog<br />\n就自然揾到4個ans各自嘅in centre <br />\n再將4個in centre分別代入條eqt度<br />\nmatch到嗰個就係正確答案啦</blockquote><br />\ne.g. 用D sub入去 即sub (7,0) (0,24) (0,0)入4心programme<br />\n會得到in centre=(3,3) 再sub 入3x+4y=3p<br />\nLHS=3(3)+4(3)=21<br />\nRHS=3(7)=21<br />\n所以D係ans"},{"pid":"35191355e1f61270213b78a76fd486cfa68b0dc8","tid":378715,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:59:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實直接用4個ans代入4心prog<br />\n就自然揾到4個ans各自嘅in centre <br />\n再將4個in centre分別代入條eqt度<br />\nmatch到嗰個就係正確答案啦</blockquote><br />\ne.g. 用D sub入去 即sub (7,0) (0,24) (0,0)入4心programme<br />\n會得到in centre=(3,3) 再sub 入3x+4y=3p<br />\nLHS=3(3)+4(3)=21<br />\nRHS=3(7)=21<br />\n所以D係ans</blockquote><br />\n呢種方法係純粹靠撳機sub數<br />\n連4心特性都可以唔駛識<br />\n而且撳機點睇都快過畫圖好多"},{"pid":"284a3967b2636fa4d5c5d82f8a5a962cf19d6f52","tid":378715,"uid":126679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:00:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實直接用4個ans代入4心prog<br />\n就自然揾到4個ans各自嘅in centre <br />\n再將4個in centre分別代入條eqt度<br />\nmatch到嗰個就係正確答案啦</blockquote><br />\ne.g. 用D sub入去 即sub (7,0) (0,24) (0,0)入4心programme<br />\n會得到in centre=(3,3) 再sub 入3x+4y=3p<br />\nLHS=3(3)+4(3)=21<br />\nRHS=3(7)=21<br />\n所以D係ans</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個方法絕對可取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但因為我就唔建議學生入4心program<br />\n所以冇係度同大家分享"},{"pid":"ee73dc55d6daedff80f847113acc6d6a08454571","tid":378715,"uid":119148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:08:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實直接用4個ans代入4心prog<br />\n就自然揾到4個ans各自嘅in centre <br />\n再將4個in centre分別代入條eqt度<br />\nmatch到嗰個就係正確答案啦</blockquote><br />\ne.g. 用D sub入去 即sub (7,0) (0,24) (0,0)入4心programme<br />\n會得到in centre=(3,3) 再sub 入3x+4y=3p<br />\nLHS=3(3)+4(3)=21<br />\nRHS=3(7)=21<br />\n所以D係ans</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個方法絕對可取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但因為我就唔建議學生入4心program<br />\n所以冇係度同大家分享</blockquote><br />\n巴打點解唔建議學生入4心program<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d3c71157895354d02eddc4916643eff0cffa26","tid":378715,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:11:15.000Z","msg":"巴打做開補習？有無telegram睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2db94a32ff583cbec65337f1c2cbc4dcb96e75","tid":378715,"uid":126679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:20:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實直接用4個ans代入4心prog<br />\n就自然揾到4個ans各自嘅in centre <br />\n再將4個in centre分別代入條eqt度<br />\nmatch到嗰個就係正確答案啦</blockquote><br />\ne.g. 用D sub入去 即sub (7,0) (0,24) (0,0)入4心programme<br />\n會得到in centre=(3,3) 再sub 入3x+4y=3p<br />\nLHS=3(3)+4(3)=21<br />\nRHS=3(7)=21<br />\n所以D係ans</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個方法絕對可取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但因為我就唔建議學生入4心program<br />\n所以冇係度同大家分享</blockquote><br />\n巴打點解唔建議學生入4心program<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有學生 / 補習老師 都覺得入得多program會計得快<br />\n的確會<br />\n但前題係你要記得邊d program打邊d program<br />\n同埋最重要有d 咩output<br />\n<br />\n坦白講<br />\n我平時教, 已經入左4條<br />\n如果要再加4心, 即係要多一部計數機<br />\n好, 當你真係有多一部<br />\n入埋4心, 咁你同時就要記埋8個output既位置<br />\n(我知有老師係教人入8條勁長既program)<br />\n<br />\n我承認<br />\n處理2017年Q41<br />\n你有4心program的確係會好快好快好快做完<br />\n但其實睇返咁多年CE + DSE<br />\n我都唔認為呢一條program係值得入<br />\n( 考親座標 我都係會叫學生拎格仔紙做<br />\n同既時間一樣可以好快)<br />\n<br />\n咁當然其實冇絕對<br />\n各人有各人長處<br />\n可能有人記性特別好<br />\n但今年考完4心, 之後個個入program<br />\n到下年又唔考<br />\n其實都冇乜意思<br />\n<br />\n所以 我呢d短片既分享<br />\n其實我既目標唔係鬥快<br />\n只係希望大家啱多一條兩條既姐"},{"pid":"e91b3e7c2231a9b28f7b1c34fddd08abd3950f97","tid":378715,"uid":126679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:22:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打做開補習？有無telegram睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\ntelegram冇乜野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔介意可以去fb page inbox我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127d168d8aa7ea6929c96158d7fcfe97b148f126","tid":378715,"uid":119148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:31:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實直接用4個ans代入4心prog<br />\n就自然揾到4個ans各自嘅in centre <br />\n再將4個in centre分別代入條eqt度<br />\nmatch到嗰個就係正確答案啦</blockquote><br />\ne.g. 用D sub入去 即sub (7,0) (0,24) (0,0)入4心programme<br />\n會得到in centre=(3,3) 再sub 入3x+4y=3p<br />\nLHS=3(3)+4(3)=21<br />\nRHS=3(7)=21<br />\n所以D係ans</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個方法絕對可取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但因為我就唔建議學生入4心program<br />\n所以冇係度同大家分享</blockquote><br />\n巴打點解唔建議學生入4心program<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有學生 / 補習老師 都覺得入得多program會計得快<br />\n的確會<br />\n但前題係你要記得邊d program打邊d program<br />\n同埋最重要有d 咩output<br />\n<br />\n坦白講<br />\n我平時教, 已經入左4條<br />\n如果要再加4心, 即係要多一部計數機<br />\n好, 當你真係有多一部<br />\n入埋4心, 咁你同時就要記埋8個output既位置<br />\n(我知有老師係教人入8條勁長既program)<br />\n<br />\n我承認<br />\n處理2017年Q41<br />\n你有4心program的確係會好快好快好快做完<br />\n但其實睇返咁多年CE + DSE<br />\n我都唔認為呢一條program係值得入<br />\n( 考親座標 我都係會叫學生拎格仔紙做<br />\n同既時間一樣可以好快)<br />\n<br />\n咁當然其實冇絕對<br />\n各人有各人長處<br />\n可能有人記性特別好<br />\n但今年考完4心, 之後個個入program<br />\n到下年又唔考<br />\n其實都冇乜意思<br />\n<br />\n所以 我呢d短片既分享<br />\n其實我既目標唔係鬥快<br />\n只係希望大家啱多一條兩條既姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當年我就係DSE MC用兩部計數機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都啱嘅 用唔慣手到時仲衰<br />\n而且教人畫圖做  真係好事嚟嘅<br />\n我見好多人做到唔識做 都唔會去諗畫圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d0b43ecfdc4375c60a19c145b226ecb900655b3","tid":378715,"uid":126679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:38:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當年我就係DSE MC用兩部計數機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都啱嘅 用唔慣手到時仲衰<br />\n而且教人畫圖做  真係好事嚟嘅<br />\n我見好多人做到唔識做 都唔會去諗畫圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實坊間解呢條都有好多唔同方法<br />\n我今次拍, 都係想再提供多一個方法比學生知道<br />\n<br />\n考數學 同上連登都差不多<br />\n有圖有真相<br />\n有左幅圖, 好多座標幾何題目都好容易解決<br />\n<br />\nbtw我有一年試過特登帶多一部計數機試下張枱夠唔夠大<br />\n結果可能我論盡<br />\n全情係咁跌野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b10c2e6279525412b797fccd752e276bfe3cde2","tid":378715,"uid":81859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:40:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/29/023823_7ce18cfbed269ad563aac7e05b2ae978.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F29%2F023823_7ce18cfbed269ad563aac7e05b2ae978.jpg&h=7ee7ad0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最正宗做法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  半分鐘ko"},{"pid":"20a390ed1180ab7044f9ec2f05c3572010c86359","tid":378715,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T19:39: